    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Exercices Semaine 2\"\nformat:\n  html:\n    html-math-method: mathjax\n    includes:\n      in_header: |\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\" async\n          src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\">\n        </script>\ntoc: false\n\neditor: source\n---\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- JavaScript -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\nfunction toggleAlert(event, message, type) {\n  var alertBox = event.target.nextElementSibling; // Select the alert box next to the clicked button\n  var alertMessage = alertBox.querySelector(\".alertMessage\");\n  var alertType = alertBox.querySelector(\".alertType\");\n\n  if (alertBox.style.display === \"block\") {\n    alertBox.style.display = \"none\"; // Hide the alert box if it's already visible\n  } else {\n    alertMessage.innerHTML = message;\n    alertType.innerHTML = (type === 'hint') ? '‚ùì Indice' : 'üí° Explication';\n\n    // Change style based on type (yellow for hint, green for explanation)\n    alertBox.style.backgroundColor = (type === 'hint') ? '#FFEDA3' : '#C0EDC2';  \n    alertBox.style.borderColor = (type === 'hint') ? '#E5B800' : '#388E3C';  \n    alertBox.style.display = \"block\";  // Show the alert\n\n    MathJax.typesetPromise([alertMessage]);  // Re-render math with MathJax v3\n  }\n}\n</script>\n\n<!-- CSS for Styling -->\n<style>\n/* Custom styles for the buttons */\n.custom-button {\n  border: none;\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: black;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.1s ease;\n}\n\n/* Green button for Explanation */\n.explanation {\n  background: #C0EDC2; /* Green */\n  border: 2px solid #388E3C; /* Slightly darker green */\n}\n\n.explanation:hover {\n  background: #388E3C; /* Darker green */\n  transform: scale(1.08);\n}\n\n/* Yellow button for Hint */\n.hint {\n  background: #FFEDA3; /* Yellow */\n  border: 2px solid #E5B800; /* Slightly darker yellow */\n}\n\n.hint:hover {\n  background: #E5B800; /* Darker yellow */\n  transform: scale(1.08);\n}\n\n/* Custom styles for the alert box */\n.alert {\n  padding: 15px;\n  color: black;\n  margin-top: 10px; /* Ensure spacing between button and alert */\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  border: 2px solid;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  width: fit-content; /* Prevent full-width alerts */\n}\n</style>\n\n<!-- MathJax for Rendering Math -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" async\n  src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/3.2.2/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\">\n</script>\n\n\n\n## Question 1\nQuelle est la r√®gle du compl√©ment en probabilit√© ?\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_UYNXVJYGNM'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_UYNXVJYGNM\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( P(A) = P(A^c) \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_UYNXVJYGNM\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>  \\\\( P(A) = 1 - P(A^c) \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_UYNXVJYGNM\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( P(A^c) = P(A) \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_UYNXVJYGNM\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( P(A^c) = P(A) + P(B) \\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pensez √† la probabilit√© totale de \\\\(1\\\\).', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'La r√®gle du compl√©ment stipule que la probabilit√© de l\\'√©v√©nement compl√©mentaire \\\\(A^C\\\\) est \\\\(1-P(A)\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Question 2\n\nSi deux √©v√©nements \\\\( A \\\\) et \\\\( B \\\\) sont mutuellement exclusifs, alors:\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_OUQDFSOIUR'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OUQDFSOIUR\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(P(A) + P(B) - P(A \\\\cap  B) > 1\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OUQDFSOIUR\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(P(A|B) = 0\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OUQDFSOIUR\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(P(B|A) = P(B)\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OUQDFSOIUR\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(P(A \\\\cap B) > 0\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Deux √©v√©nements sont mutuellement exclusifs s\\'ils ne peuvent pas se produire en m√™me temps. Cela signifie que leur intersection est vide.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'La probabilit√© conditionnelle \\\\(P(A‚à£B)\\\\) est la probabilit√© que \\\\(A\\\\) se produise sachant que \\\\(B\\\\) s\\'est produit. Puisque \\\\(A\\\\)  et \\\\(B\\\\) ne peuvent pas se produire ensemble, \\\\(P(A‚à£B)=P(A‚à£B)=0\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Question 3\nUn joueur lance deux d√©s. Quelle est la probabilit√© d‚Äôobtenir au moins un \\\\(6\\\\) sachant que la somme est \\\\(8\\\\) ?\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_KQDONLVSMF'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_KQDONLVSMF\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{1}{3} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_KQDONLVSMF\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>  \\\\( \\\\frac{2}{5} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_KQDONLVSMF\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{2}{3} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_KQDONLVSMF\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Quelles sont les paires dont la somme est \\\\(8\\\\)?', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Les paires de d√©s donnant une somme de \\\\(8\\\\) sont \\\\((2,6), (6,2), (3,5), (5,3), (4,4) \\\\). Parmi elles, \\\\(2\\\\) ont un \\\\(6\\\\), soit \\\\(\\\\frac{2}{5}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n## Question 4\n\nOn consid√®re un univers o√π \\\\(100\\\\) personnes ont √©t√© interrog√©es sur leur consommation de caf√© et de th√©. \\\\(60\\\\) boivent du caf√©, \\\\(40\\\\) boivent du th√© et \\\\(20\\\\) boivent les deux. Quelle est la probabilit√© qu‚Äôune personne choisie au hasard boive du caf√© ou du th√© ?\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_YYQJTZDNPF'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_YYQJTZDNPF\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{70}{100} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_YYQJTZDNPF\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{80}{100} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_YYQJTZDNPF\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{60}{100} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_YYQJTZDNPF\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{90}{100} \\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pensez √† la r√®gle de l\\'union des probabilit√©s.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisation de la r√®gle de l‚Äôunion des probabilit√©s : \\\\( P(C \\\\cup T) = P(C) + P(T) - P(C \\\\cap T) \\\\), soit \\\\( \\\\frac{60}{100} + \\\\frac{40}{100} - \\\\frac{20}{100} = \\\\frac{80}{100}\\\\)', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Question 5\n\nConsid√©rez la s√©rie suivante: \n\n\\\\(S_n = \\\\sum_{k=1}^{n} \\\\frac{ (-1)^k }{ k^2 }\\\\)\n\nQuelle est la valeur de \\\\(S_5\\\\)?\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_ZVDJOIUHMI'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZVDJOIUHMI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( - \\\\frac{3000}{3650} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZVDJOIUHMI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{25}{450} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZVDJOIUHMI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( - \\\\frac{125}{865} \\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZVDJOIUHMI\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\( - \\\\frac{3019}{3600} \\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, '√âcrivez chacun des termes.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, '\\\\(S_5 = -\\\\frac{1}{1^2} + \\\\frac{1}{2^2} - \\\\frac{1}{ 3^2 } + \\\\frac{1}{4^2} - \\\\frac{1}{25} = -\\\\frac{3019}{3600} \\\\)', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n---\n\n\n**Jeu avec probabilit√©s**\n\nUn jeu de soci√©t√© propose une √©preuve o√π un joueur doit tirer **au hasard** une boule d‚Äôun sac. \n\nLe sac contient **5 types de boules**, chacune ayant une valeur de points diff√©rente et une probabilit√© sp√©cifique d‚Äô√™tre tir√©e :\n\n| Type de boule | Valeur (points) | Probabilit√© |\n|--------------|-----------------|-------------|\n| \\\\(A\\\\) | \\\\(2\\\\) points | \\\\(0.1\\\\) |\n| \\\\(B\\\\) | \\\\(4\\\\) points | \\\\(0.2\\\\) |\n| \\\\(C\\\\) | \\\\(6\\\\) points | \\\\(0.3\\\\) |\n| \\\\(D\\\\) | \\\\(8\\\\) points | \\\\(0.25\\\\) |\n| \\\\(E\\\\) | \\\\(10\\\\) points | \\\\(0.15\\\\) |\n\n\n## Question 6\n\nQuelle est l‚Äôesp√©rance du nombre de points obtenus en tirant une boule au hasard ?\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_HNPFRHAXDK'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_HNPFRHAXDK\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(5.3\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_HNPFRHAXDK\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(6.2\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_HNPFRHAXDK\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(6.5\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_HNPFRHAXDK\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(6.3\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisez la formule de l‚Äôesp√©rance : \\\\(E(X) = \\\\sum_{\\\\text{tout }k} k P(X=k)\\\\) o√π \\\\(k\\\\) correspond √† un type de boule.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'L‚Äôesp√©rance se calcule par : \\\\(E(X) = (2 \\\\times 0.1) + (4 \\\\times 0.2) + (6 \\\\times 0.3) + (8 \\\\times 0.25) + (10 \\\\times 0.15) = 6.3\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 7\n\nQuelle est la probabilit√© d'obtenir une boule valant \\\\(6\\\\) points ou plus ?\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_IZMPISAWOQ'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_IZMPISAWOQ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.3\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_IZMPISAWOQ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.6\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_IZMPISAWOQ\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.7\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_IZMPISAWOQ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(1.0\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisez la formule fondamentale de la probabilit√©.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'On cherche \\\\(P(X\\\\geq6)=P(6)+P(8)+P(10)=0.3 + 0.25 + 0.15 = 0.7\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n**Probabilit√©s et organisations internationales**\n\nUne √©tude a √©t√© r√©alis√©e sur la participation des pays membres √† diff√©rentes organisations internationales. On consid√®re qu‚Äôun pays peut appartenir √† plusieurs organisations √† la fois. Un √©chantillon de \\\\(200\\\\) pays a donn√© les r√©sultats suivants (donn√©es fictives) :\n\n- **\\\\(120\\\\) pays** sont membres de l‚Äô**ONU**.\n- **\\\\(90\\\\) pays** sont membres de l‚Äô**OMC**.\n- **\\\\(60\\\\) pays** sont membres de l‚Äô**Union Africaine**.\n- **\\\\(50\\\\) pays** sont membres √† la fois de l‚ÄôONU et de l‚ÄôOMC.\n- **\\\\(30\\\\) pays** sont membres √† la fois de l‚ÄôONU et de l‚ÄôUnion Africaine.\n- **\\\\(20\\\\) pays** sont membres √† la fois de l‚ÄôOMC et de l‚ÄôUnion Africaine.\n- **\\\\(10\\\\) pays** sont membres des trois organisations.\n\n## Question 8 \n\nQuelle est la probabilit√© qu‚Äôun pays choisi au hasard soit membre de l‚ÄôONU ou de l‚ÄôOMC ?\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_QQPSTFXHXE'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_QQPSTFXHXE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.75\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_QQPSTFXHXE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.85\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_QQPSTFXHXE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(1.10\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_QQPSTFXHXE\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.80\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisez la formule de l‚Äôunion des probabilit√©s.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'La probabilit√© qu‚Äôun pays soit membre de l‚ÄôONU ou de l‚ÄôOMC est donn√©e par : \\\\( P(A \\\\cup B) = P(A) + P(B) - P(A \\\\cap B) \\\\). En rempla√ßant : \\\\( \\\\frac{120}{200} + \\\\frac{90}{200} - \\\\frac{50}{200} = 0.80 \\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 9\n\nQuelle est la probabilit√© qu‚Äôun pays choisi au hasard soit membre de l‚ÄôONU mais pas de l‚ÄôOMC ni de l‚ÄôUnion Africaine ?\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_PVVRSLEJAJ'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PVVRSLEJAJ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.20\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PVVRSLEJAJ\" value=\"answer\"><